	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This quest takes place in Innothule Swamp and is available only to evil characters.You must find an NPC named Lyguna in the swamp who randomly hide places, so you might have a problem there unless you have a ranger helping out. Lyguna is needing a ruby(the kind you can buy at any gem shop). Give Lyguna the ruby and you will receive one of three items in return. Two of these are weapons(Midnight Mallet and Bruthechopper) the other is a great earring for casters(6 int 6 wis and charges of a very nice necromancer spell). <BR>
<BR>
Brutechopper<BR>
<BR>
This weapon has a dmg of 16, a delay of 50 and weighs 11. It can be wielded by melee types of all large races as well as dwarves. <BR>
For Warriors, Paladins, Shadow Knights and Rangers.  It's 2hs.<BR>
<BR>
Midnight Mallet<BR>
<BR>
It had a dmg of 14, delay of 44 and weighs 11.<BR>
For Clerics and Shamans only.<BR>
Barbarian, Dwarve, Troll and Ogre<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
