				****CAUTION SPOILER*****<BR>
to do this quest simply find a female troll in innothule who wanders about named Lynguna... I found her twice near the guk entrance. U must give her a ruby which will cost u 138pp+ from a merchant. Not a lot of jewelery merchants sell them(qeynos, felwithe, and neriak come to mind). Simply give her the ruby and shell give u one of 3 items randomly: Brutechopper(magic 2h slash that sucks), the midnight mallet, or a magic earing(VERY good from what i hear, for shaman types).
